						"description":"A premium metallic material featuring a hammered and pebbled aluminum surface with highly reflective qualities. This material simulates industrial and decorative metalwork, offering irregular dimpled geometry and a cool, silver-gray color palette. The texture highlights light reflections and shadow gradients, creating dimensionality and depth throughout the surface. The pebbled finish balances between a rugged handcrafted look and polished sophistication, making it ideal for modern product designs, kitchenware, architectural panels, and contemporary art pieces requiring metallic realism and a unique tactile appearance.",
